The '''field kit''' was a prepared collection of assorted survival equipment  contained in a [[Backpack/Legends|backpack]]. The kits typically contained two [[condensing canteen]]s with built-in purification systems, a [[Sunshield fabric|sunshield roll]], a [[Standard week/Legends|week's]] worth of [[food rations]], two [[Glowrod/Legends|glowrods]], two [[Breath mask/Legends|breath masks]] with twenty four filters and twelve [[atmospheric canister]]s, and an [[All-Temperature Cloak|all-temperature cloak]].<ref name="RPG-Core">''[[Star Wars Roleplaying Game Core Rulebook]]''</ref>

A field kit that contained the standard collection of supplies weighed between seven<ref name="RPG-Core" /> and ten [[Kilogram/Legends|kilograms]].<ref name="RPG-Core-Rev">''[[Star Wars Roleplaying Game Revised Core Rulebook]]''</ref> From [[32 BBY/Legends|32 BBY]] to [[8 ABY/Legends|8 ABY]], the market price was between 500<ref name="RPG-Core" /> and 1,000 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]].<ref name="RPG-Core-Rev" />

